clusterList.phrase: i don't expect a new subscriber to take it all in and understand it all on the first reading or even in the first few months of readings the stock market and its language is a 60-year learning experience for me and how in the world can anyone absorb it all in one or 10 or 20 readings new subscribers need to have patience to read the sites and work on it for three or four months or preferably for a year and by that time a lot of what i'm writing and a lot of chart-reading should make sense
